</b>128.107 <b>Take measures to ensure the effective implementation of programmes 
to protect children&#8217;s rights at the local level, particularly as regards violence, 
commercial sexual exploitation and child labour (Belgium);  
</b>128.108 <b>Take steps to prevent violence against children, in particular in 
school, family and penitentiary environments, and engage effectively in the 
